{
  "scene_id": "vaelith_ember_vein",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_001",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Ah. You made it out. I was beginning to wonder."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_002",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Please. If I wanted to stop you, I wouldn't have\nwaited up here in the cold."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": [
        {
          "who": "edren",
          "anim": "bubble_exclaim",
          "when": "before_line_0"
        }
      ],
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_003",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "My name is Vaelith. I study old places — ruins,\nmostly. I've been watching this mine for some time. The Compact's\nexcavation was... ambitious, if graceless."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_004",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "What do you want?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_005",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "May I see what you found?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_006",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "No."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_007",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Of course. I wouldn't trust a stranger on a cliff\nat night either."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": [
        {
          "who": "vaelith",
          "anim": "nod",
          "when": "before_line_0"
        }
      ],
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_008",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "What a fragile little thing it is to build hope\naround."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_009",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "We're taking it to Valdris."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_010",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Naturally. Safe journey, then. The trail west is\nclear — the soldiers are focused on the mine entrance."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_011",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Do take care of yourself, Cael. Old places do\nstrange things to sensitive minds."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_012",
      "speaker": "cael",
      "lines": [
        "How do you know my—"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": [
        {
          "who": "cael",
          "anim": "step_back",
          "when": "before_line_0"
        }
      ],
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_013",
      "speaker": "cael",
      "lines": [
        "He knew my name. I didn't—"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_014",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "I know. We didn't tell him."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_015",
      "speaker": "cael",
      "lines": [
        "And he knew the mine route. And that we'd come out\nthis way. And he didn't try to take the Pendulum."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "vaelith_ember_vein_016",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "Which means either he doesn't want it, or he doesn't\nneed to take it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    }
  ]
}
